<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Payment Action Required</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    .wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 40px 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #0f172a;
      padding: 32px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 32px;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #1e293b;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    p {
      color: #475569;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 24px;
      margin-top: 0;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .alert-box {
      background-color: #fef2f2;
      border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .alert-title {
      color: #991b1b;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .alert-desc {
      color: #ef4444;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .details-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .details-table td {
      padding: 12px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .label {
      color: #64748b;
      font-weight: 500;
      width: 150px;
    }
    .value {
      color: #0f172a;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-align: right;
    }
    .btn-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 32px 0 16px 0;
    }
    .btn {
      background-color: #ef4444;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2);
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      padding: 24px 32px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
    }
    .footer-text {
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 18px;
      margin: 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">SaaS Subscription</div>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h1>Payment Action Required</h1>
        <p>Hello {{customerName}},</p>
        <p>We were unable to process the subscription payment for your plan. There seems to be an issue with your registered card details.</p>
        
        <div class="alert-box">
          <div class="alert-title">Failure Reason</div>
          <div class="alert-desc">{{failureReason}}</div>
        </div>

        <table class="details-table">
          <tr>
            <td class="label">Plan</td>
            <td class="value">{{planName}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="label">Amount Due</td>
            <td class="value">{{amount}}</td>
          </tr>
          {{#if nextRetryDate}}
          <tr>
            <td class="label">Next Retry Date</td>
            <td class="value">{{nextRetryDate}}</td>
          </tr>
          {{/if}}
        </table>

        <p>To avoid service interruptions or restriction of your subscription features, please update your billing method as soon as possible.</p>

        <div class="btn-container">
          <a href="{{updateCardUrl}}" class="btn">Update Payment Method</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p class="footer-text">
          If you have any questions, please contact our support team.<br>
          &copy; 2026 SaaS Inc. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
